        <h2 class="title"><a href="/archives/000202.html">Sermon on the Mount, as annotated by George W. Bush</a></h2>    <span class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/user/brad" title="View user profile." rel="nofollow">brad</a> on Thu, 2005-04-28 08:01.</span>
